	x2 y2 x3 y3 rarc
	x3 y3 x4 y4 rarc
	x4 y4 x1 y1 rarc
	x1 y1 x2 y2 rarc
	closepath
	} stopped
	 {x1 y1 x2 y2 x3 y3 x4 y4 newpath moveto lineto lineto lineto closepath} if
	cleartomark
